title: Evan Geiselman 2014 Part | Presented by Neff
description:
Evan Geiselman travels the world in search of some fun little waves.

We'll be launching one video a day for each of our team riders - Nov. 10th-14th. Check out Kolohe Andino, Dion Agius, Evan Geiselman, Jordy Smith, and Noah Beschen get wild on StabMag.com.

Neff was the first authentic core snow and skate headwear company in the world. Neff is supported by some of the globe's biggest action sports athletes and key personalities in music and sports. We're all about having fun and bringing new vibes to the world.

“We are like a gumball machine; spitting out endless flavors for the world to consume,” said Shaun Neff. We are not confined to one specific category; we are defined by reaching across multiple platforms like sports, fashion and entertainment.
